WEBVTT

02:58.520 --> 02:59.600
Thank you.

03:05.920 --> 03:09.160
You're not some young couple anymore.
Why are you thanking him?

03:10.680 --> 03:12.200
Let's get out of here first.

03:14.000 --> 03:15.160
Fine.

03:19.320 --> 03:20.840
I'll trust you for now.

03:22.400 --> 03:23.600
I agree to work with you.

03:24.880 --> 03:26.280
You can take the others.

03:27.640 --> 03:28.960
But not Lu Wuyi.

03:29.720 --> 03:30.680
Why?

03:31.640 --> 03:34.840
She matters to me more than anyone.

03:36.040 --> 03:38.520
Among the relics left in the Ruined Sand,

03:38.600 --> 03:41.800
there's a portrait of a mortal woman
named Di Zhu.

03:42.640 --> 03:46.200
Lu Wuyi looks exactly like her.

03:46.960 --> 03:48.360
From the moment
she was born in the Sacred Spring,

03:49.000 --> 03:52.280
you shaped her face like Di Zhu's.

03:53.000 --> 03:55.920
I never understood this before.
You're Jiu Ying.

03:56.480 --> 03:58.640
You shouldn't be able to obtain

03:58.720 --> 04:00.360
their memories
from the Primordial Sacred Spring.

04:01.040 --> 04:02.600
But now I see.

04:02.680 --> 04:07.600
You created Lu Wuyi to gather
everyone's emotions and memories.

04:08.440 --> 04:10.560
Thus, you controlled
the entire Formless Moon Sect.

04:10.640 --> 04:13.840
You made up the lie of a "fated one"

04:13.920 --> 04:15.640
and sent her to get close to me.

04:17.040 --> 04:18.120
What?

04:19.040 --> 04:20.320
Now that your plan works,

04:21.720 --> 04:23.600
you want to take her back from me?

04:24.240 --> 04:25.560
The plan works?

04:27.200 --> 04:28.760
You actually think Lu Wuyi likes you?

04:31.520 --> 04:36.400
Then why not let her stay with me

04:38.400 --> 04:39.400
and keep watching me?

04:48.680 --> 04:52.520
I'll take all of them with me.

04:56.440 --> 04:59.280
You're nothing more than leftovers

04:59.360 --> 05:02.360
after I devoured
your memories and spat you out.

05:03.320 --> 05:08.240
It was only my power
that gave you this new body.

05:09.200 --> 05:11.480
You've always wanted to know who you are,

05:12.320 --> 05:14.640
but Bai Ze and Chi Wen,

05:15.320 --> 05:19.480
who knew the truth all along,
kept it from you.

05:20.600 --> 05:22.360
Your Master Dragon Deity

05:23.120 --> 05:26.760
knew your confusion and your doubts,

05:27.880 --> 05:30.280
and yet he said nothing.

05:30.360 --> 05:33.880
He simply let you go on
playing the commander,

05:33.960 --> 05:38.720
serving him, fighting for him,
and dying for him.

05:40.720 --> 05:42.040
Just like

05:44.400 --> 05:46.040
he did with Ji Ling.

05:49.920 --> 05:51.400
How pitiful.

05:56.120 --> 05:58.320
I have one more secret to tell you.

06:00.120 --> 06:01.000
Come closer.

06:21.560 --> 06:23.280
This body

06:25.160 --> 06:27.040
won't last much longer.

06:30.440 --> 06:33.640
Heavenly Sticks can see fate and destiny.

06:33.720 --> 06:36.080
Prying into fate comes at a cost.

06:36.680 --> 06:40.520
Every divination must be paid
for with one's own power and lifespan.

06:42.560 --> 06:44.400
Since you're here,

06:49.520 --> 06:51.600
shall we exchange bodies?

08:34.080 --> 08:38.919
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

09:01.200 --> 09:04.400
Wangyan, what do we do next?

09:07.880 --> 09:09.760
Destroy the Oracle Stone.

09:10.480 --> 09:12.920
Kill Jiu Ying, who's attached to it.

09:17.040 --> 09:18.520
But when the next full moon comes,

09:19.120 --> 09:21.400
we'll still be summoned back
to the Formless Moon Sect.

09:23.520 --> 09:26.920
If we fail before then…

09:28.640 --> 09:29.640
We'll have

09:32.280 --> 09:33.160
to sever our tails.

09:45.960 --> 09:49.440
Looks like he knows who he is now.

09:51.240 --> 09:53.120
I know who I am too.

10:24.160 --> 10:25.840
Body returns to dust.

10:26.480 --> 10:28.320
Spirit is carried away by the wind.

10:30.120 --> 10:32.400
May you be freed from your obsessions,

10:33.040 --> 10:36.640
and in your next life, live long, healthy,

10:38.760 --> 10:40.000
and in peace.

10:45.440 --> 10:50.200
You left your blade
in Ruined Sand, didn't you?

11:01.720 --> 11:03.320
I'll go with you.

11:32.520 --> 11:36.080
I should've brought it back
to the Shilin Sect for you.

11:37.080 --> 11:41.200
But no one but you can wield
the Mountain Demon Blade.

11:45.760 --> 11:47.040
Go retrieve it.

11:51.840 --> 11:53.120
Is there a problem?

12:10.480 --> 12:13.440
That six-eyed butterfly demon
called himself Yuan Wuhuo.

12:14.400 --> 12:17.600
He looks exactly like Commander Li.

12:31.080 --> 12:32.160
What is it?

12:37.880 --> 12:38.880
Nothing.

12:39.920 --> 12:41.280
It reminded me of back then,

12:41.360 --> 12:45.280
when you sent me to Mount Nandang
to pull out the blade.

12:45.360 --> 12:48.680
That's how I got this weapon,
which has stayed by my side ever since.

13:43.960 --> 13:45.080
I've checked it.

13:45.920 --> 13:47.560
He's not Yuan Wuhuo.

13:48.880 --> 13:50.200
That's good.

13:50.720 --> 13:52.160
What about you?

13:52.880 --> 13:54.000
Are you alright?

13:57.760 --> 13:59.080
You know full well

14:00.040 --> 14:03.720
the Dragon Deity's Power has long blended
with your own demon power.

14:04.520 --> 14:08.240
If you try to separate it,
the backlash will be fatal.

14:08.920 --> 14:10.080
You can't be saved.

14:12.640 --> 14:15.400
I've given all my demon power
to protect my inner core.

14:16.480 --> 14:19.600
I can still hold on a little longer.

14:35.880 --> 14:39.240
I want to walk
this final journey with you.

14:42.040 --> 14:43.320
Don't worry about me.

14:44.520 --> 14:46.040
Wu Shiguang is waiting for you.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.280
Go to Luo'an.

14:54.880 --> 14:57.840
Take back the last trace
of Dragon Deity's Power from Han Ba.

15:35.960 --> 15:36.920
Wangyan,

15:38.120 --> 15:41.800
what kind of secret
do the two dragons share?

15:41.880 --> 15:43.640
Why did they hide it from us?

15:45.680 --> 15:49.320
Probably just something between men.

15:51.720 --> 15:53.080
Don't overthink it.

15:53.160 --> 15:56.080
We've kept plenty from them too.

16:08.560 --> 16:11.960
You came all this way because
you heard I was captured by Jiu Ying?

16:13.520 --> 16:16.560
I was worried you'd get skinned
and turned into a fox-fur coat.

16:16.640 --> 16:18.640
Too bad I was late.

16:18.720 --> 16:21.120
Missed my chance to play the hero.

16:22.160 --> 16:25.240
Hero, what's your name?

16:26.360 --> 16:27.200
Call me sister.

16:29.840 --> 16:31.560
I only have one sister.

16:32.400 --> 16:34.520
Greedy Wolf Demon Hunter
of the Northern Dipper. Si Feng.

16:36.520 --> 16:38.040
I can tell.

16:38.120 --> 16:40.880
That double-flower mark
on her forehead is hard to miss.

16:41.560 --> 16:43.200
Since when did
a thousand-year-old fox like you

16:43.800 --> 16:48.760
get so close to a ruthless demon hunter
from the Big Dipper?

16:48.840 --> 16:50.160
I didn't know that.

16:53.960 --> 16:55.840
Honestly, neither did I.

16:58.840 --> 17:00.160
What has happened?

17:15.680 --> 17:17.480
Were you waiting for me?

17:17.560 --> 17:18.920
I was.

17:22.599 --> 17:24.160
And you are?

17:25.359 --> 17:26.880
What's the matter?

17:27.760 --> 17:29.040
You're at it again.

17:29.120 --> 17:31.880
We've met before. Many times.

17:33.160 --> 17:36.280
If I'd met someone
as powerful as you that often,

17:36.360 --> 17:37.640
I wouldn't have forgotten.

17:37.720 --> 17:39.160
What if your memory was erased?

17:40.760 --> 17:42.640
Master Chi Wen left you a message.

17:43.160 --> 17:45.360
The Oracle Stone can't be trusted.

17:46.040 --> 17:47.400
If you have doubts,

17:47.480 --> 17:50.080
seal away part of your memory
inside this artifact.

17:50.160 --> 17:53.440
Retrieve it later,
and it'll remind you of the truth.

18:03.640 --> 18:05.160
Let me remind you of something.

18:05.240 --> 18:08.480
The first time we met
was because of Han Ba.

18:10.360 --> 18:11.480
Han Ba?

18:16.040 --> 18:17.480
Have you figured out

18:18.080 --> 18:21.800
why Jiu Ying erased the memory
of our first meeting?

18:23.320 --> 18:24.360
No.

18:25.720 --> 18:29.040
I only know I was on a mission.

18:29.640 --> 18:30.640
A mission?

18:32.520 --> 18:35.880
We always act together.
We've never taken solo missions.

18:36.480 --> 18:38.400
That's strange.

18:38.480 --> 18:43.120
But we're heading
to Luo'an soon to find Han Ba.

18:43.200 --> 18:46.720
When we get there,
we'll get to the bottom of this.

18:48.520 --> 18:51.840
I've seen all of Chi Wen's memories.

18:54.040 --> 18:55.920
What did you see?

18:57.360 --> 19:01.120
<i>No one here should sacrifice yourselves.</i>
<i>There's another way.</i>

19:01.720 --> 19:04.640
<i>Just lend me your demon power.</i>

19:04.720 --> 19:09.600
<i>As for returning the deity power,</i>
<i>I have my own plan.</i>

19:11.080 --> 19:12.480
You're free.

19:13.400 --> 19:15.360
Your will is your own.

19:15.920 --> 19:18.720
Whether you choose
slaughter or protection,

19:19.520 --> 19:20.920
that's up to you.

19:22.160 --> 19:27.640
<i>Fuse our reverse scales together</i>
<i>and create the Tenth Dragon Son.</i>

19:28.840 --> 19:32.600
<i>That will be</i>
<i>our final hope for this world.</i>

19:32.680 --> 19:33.920
You're not Chi Wen.

19:36.800 --> 19:38.480
And you're not my brother.

19:40.800 --> 19:44.880
<i>From now on,</i>
<i>you're neither demon nor human.</i>

19:45.600 --> 19:47.720
<i>You are Chi Wen.</i>

19:48.240 --> 19:50.720
<i>The last Dragon Deity in this world.</i>

19:51.840 --> 19:55.840
But you've been carrying
the burden my brothers left you,

19:57.040 --> 19:59.000
the hopes of the world,

20:00.680 --> 20:02.800
and a lie meant to deceive it.

20:04.240 --> 20:05.800
I know you've been waiting for me.

20:06.600 --> 20:10.120
How long must I keep lying?

20:11.040 --> 20:13.800
<i>Until the Tenth Dragon Son awakens</i>
<i>and becomes a true dragon.</i>

20:14.840 --> 20:17.640
<i>Only then will your mission end.</i>

20:18.960 --> 20:21.080
The Tenth Dragon Son?

20:28.840 --> 20:29.960
I'm sorry.

20:33.720 --> 20:35.560
I made you wait so long.

20:41.720 --> 20:44.360
It has been a long time.

20:48.880 --> 20:50.240
Too long.

20:59.920 --> 21:01.240
But at least

21:04.120 --> 21:05.240
you're here now.

21:06.640 --> 21:10.280
Once the Dragon Deity's Power is complete
and you return to your rightful place,

21:12.280 --> 21:14.480
I can finally lay this burden down.

21:17.880 --> 21:20.320
Everyone calls you Master Chi Wen.

21:21.560 --> 21:23.160
But what is your real name?

21:24.680 --> 21:29.080
Before you became
Master Dragon Deity, who were you?

21:37.720 --> 21:38.680
Ji Ling.

21:43.480 --> 21:45.000
My name

21:49.200 --> 21:50.240
is Ji Ling.

21:53.320 --> 21:57.520
Ji, as in "a fleeting life".
Ling, as in "a kindred understanding".

22:04.720 --> 22:07.120
Sir, what's your name?

22:07.200 --> 22:08.400
My name is Ji Ling.

22:08.480 --> 22:10.240
Ji, as in "a fleeting life".
Ling, as in "a kindred understanding".

22:35.480 --> 22:36.720
I knew it.

22:38.240 --> 22:39.400
You are Ji Ling.

22:41.400 --> 22:42.520
Ji Ling.

22:43.960 --> 22:45.320
One day,

22:47.520 --> 22:49.000
you'll admit it yourself.

22:49.520 --> 22:51.960
I'll ask you one last time.

22:53.080 --> 22:56.200
Are you Ji Ling?

22:56.800 --> 22:59.760
Give Ji Ling back to me. Give him back!

23:00.840 --> 23:05.400
Are you Ji Ling?

23:06.240 --> 23:07.160
No.

23:07.240 --> 23:08.520
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.120
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:11.520 --> 23:13.000
You are Ji Ling.

23:15.960 --> 23:17.080
You are

23:21.680 --> 23:23.160
Ji Ling.

24:21.240 --> 24:24.200
Why did you make all these puppets?

24:29.720 --> 24:33.800
Since I became the Dragon Deity,
I've rarely left the Scale Cave.

24:34.440 --> 24:40.040
The Dragon Deity may be immortal
and free to roam the world,

24:40.640 --> 24:45.280
but I… was just an ordinary fox.

24:46.360 --> 24:47.760
You're a fox too?

24:51.480 --> 24:52.600
But

24:54.280 --> 24:56.760
not a noble nine-tailed fox
from Green Hills like you.

24:57.360 --> 25:01.080
I was just a foolish red fox

25:01.840 --> 25:03.640
born by Yumian Lake.

25:11.800 --> 25:13.000
A wild fox?

25:13.840 --> 25:15.200
That's cute.

25:21.520 --> 25:24.080
If I were killed out there by demons,

25:24.160 --> 25:27.320
my disguise as the Dragon Deity
would fall apart.

25:28.440 --> 25:30.480
I've stayed in this cave so long.

25:31.840 --> 25:34.000
I keep thinking about who I used to be.

25:35.320 --> 25:39.280
Back then, I was naïve and childish.

25:41.000 --> 25:43.720
But I lived every moment sincerely.

25:44.400 --> 25:47.240
I was simpler and freer than I am now.

25:47.760 --> 25:52.120
Like the warm summer wind
brushes through the trees.

25:54.960 --> 25:58.520
Back then, I knew little,

25:59.640 --> 26:00.840
so I had fewer regrets.

26:01.840 --> 26:07.320
The worst thing was just
not getting fresh raspberries in winter.

26:09.960 --> 26:13.720
Later, I came across an old spell

26:14.280 --> 26:16.320
in the ancient scrolls of Wanlin Pavilion.

26:17.520 --> 26:18.960
It has a beautiful name.

26:20.040 --> 26:21.480
<i>Severed Silk.</i>

26:24.560 --> 26:29.680
It takes a piece of one's life
and cuts it out,

26:30.960 --> 26:34.440
like trimming fabric
and weaving patterns into silk.

26:35.480 --> 26:38.800
Once separated,
that piece becomes its own being,

26:38.880 --> 26:41.440
bearing the same appearance,

26:41.520 --> 26:43.680
personality, and memories as its owner,

26:45.520 --> 26:47.320
only without life.

27:30.040 --> 27:33.400
<i>So the Ji Ling you met</i>
<i>was created that way.</i>

27:34.120 --> 27:35.960
Are you a demon hunter
from the mortal world?

27:36.040 --> 27:37.840
I'm a demon hunter of the Shilin Sect.

27:38.760 --> 27:42.320
I sent him out to feel the mountain winds,

27:42.400 --> 27:43.800
the life of the mortal world,

27:47.120 --> 27:48.400
joy,

27:49.800 --> 27:51.080
sorrow,

27:52.320 --> 27:53.640
adventure,

27:55.320 --> 27:56.600
and love.

28:01.080 --> 28:04.760
<i>He lived that life</i>
<i>in my place to experience</i>

28:06.080 --> 28:07.480
<i>a colorful life.</i>

28:33.960 --> 28:36.280
<i>He'd go out, then return,</i>

28:37.080 --> 28:39.800
<i>bringing the lively world outside to me,</i>

28:40.960 --> 28:43.040
<i>while I stay in solitude.</i>

28:48.280 --> 28:50.360
<i>Then how did you end up</i>
<i>in the Shilin Sect?</i>

28:51.400 --> 28:53.280
How did you become the Dragon Deity?

28:55.280 --> 28:59.280
When the meteor blast happened,
the earth shook.

29:00.280 --> 29:01.760
I was blind since childhood.

29:02.880 --> 29:06.560
I couldn't see the rocks falling
and failed to escape.

29:07.080 --> 29:09.560
I was buried under rubble
at the foot of South Mountain.

29:19.200 --> 29:20.880
<i>Master Chi Wen saved me.</i>

29:21.560 --> 29:23.160
He took pity on me

29:23.840 --> 29:26.000
and said a blind little fox like me

29:26.080 --> 29:30.480
couldn't survive on my own.

29:31.640 --> 29:34.880
So he brought me to the disaster site

29:35.800 --> 29:37.920
and granted me a healing spell

29:39.680 --> 29:41.360
so that I could help others.

29:53.280 --> 29:54.400
Sadly,

29:55.720 --> 29:58.560
I was too young
and couldn't take human form.

30:00.160 --> 30:02.480
The power he gave me was limited.

30:03.080 --> 30:05.800
Once it was used up, that was it.

30:06.400 --> 30:10.120
So some people

30:12.080 --> 30:14.040
couldn't be saved.

30:15.560 --> 30:16.560
Xizai.

30:17.120 --> 30:18.080
Xizai.

30:19.000 --> 30:20.000
Xizai!

30:21.080 --> 30:22.120
Xizai!

30:22.640 --> 30:23.920
Xizai!

30:27.200 --> 30:30.880
Where's your sacred power?
Save him! Come on!

30:44.760 --> 30:47.840
Save my brother. And I'll let you go.

31:19.560 --> 31:20.920
What happened after that?

31:33.800 --> 31:36.440
Wangyan and the others are waiting for us.

31:37.520 --> 31:41.080
That story is too long.

31:41.680 --> 31:43.160
I could talk day and night
and still not finish it.

31:43.760 --> 31:47.000
Once we return from Luo'an,
I'll tell you slowly.

31:49.600 --> 31:50.680
Promise.

32:00.080 --> 32:02.600
That's childish, wild fox.

32:09.120 --> 32:10.000
In the past,

32:10.080 --> 32:13.320
only Li Jie and the Four Great Demons
knew I wasn't the Dragon Deity.

32:14.280 --> 32:17.760
Now that it's out in the open,
I actually feel a lot lighter.

32:18.440 --> 32:22.240
From now on, I'll call you Ji Ling.

32:22.960 --> 32:24.040
Is that alright?

32:31.160 --> 32:34.680
Can you give me this doll?

32:37.640 --> 32:40.320
I can trade you something else for it.

32:44.800 --> 32:48.640
This little fox
is the most precious thing I own.

32:49.640 --> 32:51.680
Nothing is worth trading for it.

32:52.360 --> 32:55.440
Back then, when I was imprisoned here,

32:55.520 --> 33:00.000
it was the one that stayed with me
through those dark days.

33:01.120 --> 33:02.400
I even thought…

33:11.640 --> 33:12.720
What was it?

33:16.560 --> 33:17.800
It saved me.

33:21.720 --> 33:24.800
When I was at my lowest, it comforted me

33:24.880 --> 33:28.480
and gave me the courage to go on.

33:31.520 --> 33:33.640
How could a rag doll comfort you?

33:33.720 --> 33:35.240
Don't tell me it talks.

33:35.840 --> 33:37.240
It really does.

33:38.640 --> 33:41.560
See? I knew you'd react like that.

33:42.280 --> 33:43.800
No one ever believes me.

33:43.880 --> 33:45.360
But it's true.

33:51.880 --> 33:55.400
Whenever my tears fell on it,

33:56.680 --> 33:59.400
it was like it could feel my sadness.

34:02.400 --> 34:04.760
It would make soft sounds like a real fox.

34:05.520 --> 34:07.240
Awu… awu…

34:08.320 --> 34:09.719
It was telling me,

34:10.960 --> 34:12.120
"Don't cry.

34:13.760 --> 34:15.159
Don't be sad.

34:16.760 --> 34:18.480
I'll stay with you."

34:22.760 --> 34:24.080
That's ridiculous.

34:24.639 --> 34:28.040
If it were real, someone
must've cast a spell on it.

34:39.320 --> 34:40.760
You're messing with me again, aren't you?

34:44.400 --> 34:45.800
I'm not lying.

34:46.880 --> 34:50.960
Maybe it's because you're here.

34:51.040 --> 34:52.280
It's shy.

34:54.600 --> 34:58.200
But I haven't heard its voice
in a long time.

35:08.480 --> 35:09.520
Here.

35:17.960 --> 35:21.680
Isn't this your most treasured thing?
You said you wouldn't trade it.

35:22.480 --> 35:25.080
That's right. I wouldn't trade it.

35:28.400 --> 35:31.760
I'm not asking for anything in return.

35:32.760 --> 35:34.560
I'm giving it to you because I want to.

35:35.600 --> 35:39.560
Right now, there's nothing
more precious to me than you.

35:41.720 --> 35:43.480
Whatever you want,

35:44.560 --> 35:46.320
I'll get it for you.

35:48.680 --> 35:51.960
I want your heart.
Will you give me that too?

35:53.400 --> 35:54.560
Yes.

35:58.400 --> 36:01.760
Master Dragon Deity,
what's gotten into you?

36:02.440 --> 36:05.640
You weren't like this before.
You've got quite a smooth tongue.

36:06.680 --> 36:10.520
I'll say whatever you want to hear.

36:10.600 --> 36:14.120
I'll do anything for you.

36:16.720 --> 36:20.160
I want the stars and the moon.

36:25.440 --> 36:26.840
I'll find a way.

36:29.640 --> 36:31.000
Master Dragon Deity,

36:32.960 --> 36:34.920
something's wrong with you.

36:37.360 --> 36:39.120
You've become a different person.

36:40.400 --> 36:41.640
I haven't changed.

36:43.080 --> 36:44.120
I'm Ji Ling.

36:53.200 --> 36:54.280
Before

36:55.720 --> 36:56.640
or now,

36:58.280 --> 37:00.360
all I ever wanted was for you to be happy.

37:56.280 --> 38:00.040
Get some rest. We leave
for Luo'an tomorrow morning.

38:01.960 --> 38:05.960
You gave me the little fox,
so I'll give you something in return.

38:07.640 --> 38:11.320
But first, close your eyes.

38:33.240 --> 38:34.080
Alright.

38:39.760 --> 38:41.040
What are you thinking about?

38:43.360 --> 38:44.360
I…

38:56.040 --> 38:57.240
I've put it on.

38:58.240 --> 38:59.720
You're not allowed
to run away in this lifetime.

39:19.920 --> 39:21.000
What is this?

39:22.640 --> 39:24.400
This is also something I treasure.

39:26.800 --> 39:28.560
They're Twin Luminous Cicadas.

39:29.720 --> 39:31.440
They come as a pair.

39:31.520 --> 39:33.480
No matter how far apart they are,

39:34.080 --> 39:37.880
if one lights up,
the other will glow as well.

39:46.680 --> 39:49.720
If you miss me, tap it.

39:51.480 --> 39:53.160
As long as I see it light up,

39:54.240 --> 39:55.560
I'll know

39:57.160 --> 39:58.360
you're thinking of me.

40:15.640 --> 40:17.960
Why has your scent grown fainter?

40:20.640 --> 40:21.960
You're being silly again.

41:11.280 --> 41:16.040
I didn't expect the Master Bai Ze
who knows all things in the world

41:17.080 --> 41:18.440
would still need to read books.

41:22.120 --> 41:25.080
I'm looking for an ancient way
to extend one's lifespan.

41:26.160 --> 41:27.640
Master Dragon Deity,
if I can't walk with you

41:28.360 --> 41:30.640
to the very end of your life,

41:32.360 --> 41:33.840
that would be my regret.

41:38.920 --> 41:40.400
You're still calling me that?

41:42.800 --> 41:44.040
In my heart,

41:45.200 --> 41:46.920
you are Master Dragon Deity.

41:53.200 --> 41:54.320
So,

41:55.960 --> 41:59.840
old man, you'd better stay alive.

42:05.440 --> 42:08.480
The last three spirit fragments
of Jiu Ying have been found.

42:09.880 --> 42:14.200
One is inside Wu Shiguang.

42:15.560 --> 42:17.720
One is inside the Oracle Stone.

42:21.280 --> 42:22.640
The last one…

42:25.840 --> 42:27.280
I've checked it.

42:29.920 --> 42:31.600
It's inside Lu Wuyi.

42:37.000 --> 42:38.520
Inside the Star Stone illusion,

42:39.680 --> 42:43.240
none of us could use our powers.

42:44.160 --> 42:48.920
But Lu Wuyi could still use
Word Magic and Frost Spell.

42:49.520 --> 42:53.200
And yet her power came and went.

42:54.040 --> 42:55.360
It was unstable.

42:56.600 --> 42:59.440
It didn't take long
for me to understand why.

42:59.520 --> 43:03.920
Only when that little snake,
Little Nine, was nearby…

43:04.000 --> 43:05.640
That's intense.

43:05.720 --> 43:07.200
<i>…could she cast her spells.</i>

43:16.000 --> 43:17.520
<i>And when Little Nine moved away,</i>

43:19.320 --> 43:20.520
<i>her power vanished.</i>

43:21.280 --> 43:22.320
What happened to my power?

43:28.520 --> 43:32.160
That little snake is Jiu Ying.

43:33.320 --> 43:38.960
So you suspect Lu Wuyi and Jiu Ying
share some unique bond,

43:39.640 --> 43:41.680
which is why she can use power?

43:41.760 --> 43:42.920
Exactly.

43:43.000 --> 43:46.040
I questioned Jiu Ying
in the Formless Moon Palace.

43:47.120 --> 43:48.960
Now I understand.

43:49.040 --> 43:50.800
You created Lu Wuyi

43:50.880 --> 43:54.480
to gather everyone's emotions
and memories.

43:55.000 --> 43:57.240
Thus, you controlled
the entire Formless Moon Sect.

43:58.920 --> 44:04.160
I've also confirmed
that the fragment is inside Lu Wuyi.

44:06.480 --> 44:07.800
I don't think

44:09.320 --> 44:12.040
I can walk this road with you to the end.

44:17.240 --> 44:18.920
Because the end…

44:21.080 --> 44:22.920
The end

44:26.760 --> 44:28.560
means Lu Wuyi's death.

44:32.480 --> 44:34.480
If we want to destroy Jiu Ying completely,

44:40.200 --> 44:41.400
Lu Wuyi

44:45.560 --> 44:46.560
must die.

44:57.480 --> 44:58.640
<i>I know</i>

45:00.640 --> 45:02.200
<i>I'm about to lose her.</i>

45:06.000 --> 45:06.920
So,

45:09.600 --> 45:11.640
I'll give her

45:15.040 --> 45:16.400
anything she wants.

45:17.280 --> 45:19.160
<i>I want your heart.</i>

45:19.240 --> 45:20.520
<i>Will you give me that too?</i>

45:21.400 --> 45:22.280
Yes.

45:23.360 --> 45:24.440
Do you know?

45:26.920 --> 45:28.480
In this world,

45:31.000 --> 45:33.040
no one can see the new moon.

45:41.560 --> 45:42.880
Only I can.

45:52.040 --> 45:53.080
She is

45:55.320 --> 45:57.080
my moon alone.
